{
  "stem": "1222.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then what happened?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We asked one of our elderly lady, what's new in Miedzyrzecz?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She said in Miedzyrzecz, there is already Jewish people sleeping the streets.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they-- they are alive, some of them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I figured we going to walk back to the city.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Coming about a half a mile from the city, was going-- was going in a bicycle two police, Ukrainian police with rifles.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They catched us.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They beat us.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They beat me up.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they beat up my friend in the face.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they tied us up for the hand, one to the other one.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we were running in the back of their bikes.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He brought us up-- I'll never forget that thing-- a heavy-- a heavy leader, a German with Nazi, [GERMAN] over their face.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And they give us two brooms and sweep the sleep.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Plus, we have to clean some of the bodies.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I came up to two people that I knew them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They were laying dead.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I was anxious to find out if mine parents-- and he was anxious, that other one, Dudela, if his parents are there.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "As soon nobody was there, of course the officer didn't come out to see, with two [INAUDIBLE], we threw away the broom.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We run.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "We run to the house.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "In my auntie's house, we were preparing ourselves.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "If we don't want to go to work, we used hide ourself in our cellar.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "We dig the cellar underneath the bed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And we were hiding there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "For it was for-- we digged it for weeks, you know, with a shovel, with everything there.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And we were there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "So I figured like that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "If I go right away into that cellar, my mother had a weak heart, she would faint.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
